  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>&quot;Patient Global Impression of Change&quot; (PGI-C) at visit 4</measure>
    <time_frame>12 weeks</time_frame>
    <description>It is the statistical comparison between the placebo group and the memantine group.The group comparison will be performed by the use of an analysis of covariance (ANCOVA) model.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
  <secondary_outcome>
    <measure>Change from baseline to visit 3 and 5 of Patient Global Impression of Change (PGI-C)</measure>
